data.description: This newly renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is ready for you and your family! Featuring new flooring throughout, new white cabinets, new granite countertops, new electricals, new decs, front and back, updated bathrooms, and new duct work. So come inside and enjoy your updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Spend time with the family in either the living room or the den. You'll love the new master bath with a new vanity cabinet, new faucet, and new walk-in shower. The level yard is perfect for outdoor activities and large deck for grilling. Vinyl framed windows. Propane gas central heat, electric air.
